# The three crew agent defs land here, one flat `agents/<role>.md` file each
# (the documented Claude Code `agents/` layout, mirroring
# `claude-plugins/kampus-pipeline/agents/`):
#
#   exec-assistant.md      — EA / chief-of-staff        (issue #2360)
#   engineering-manager.md — execution conductor         (issue #2354)
#   triage.md              — intake + planning/canon seam (issue #2355)
#
# Each is authored by its own Phase-3 child and MUST write against the
# personalization seam (../PERSONALIZATION.md) — no literal operator/machine
# detail in any def. This file only keeps the empty scaffold dir tracked; it is
# not an agent def (the loader globs `agents/*.md`, so a dotfile is ignored).
